OpenStreetMap is a free street level map of the world, created by an ever growing community of mappers.

Anyone can edit OpenStreetMap and here you can learn how. LearnOSM provides easy to understand, step by step guides for you to get started with contributing to OpenStreetMap and using OpenStreetMap data. If you're interested in running an OpenStreetMap workshop, check out the LearnOSM trainer resources.
